title: EP. 98 Royal-T of Low Profile Records Tells All
itunes:title: EP. 98 Royal-T of Low Profile Records Tells All
description:
Royal-T, the ceo of Low Profile records, who’s company has sold millions of records breaks down misunderstandings that he had with former artist Lil Rob, he also shares how he got started in the Southern California swap meets and why some artist should be more appreciative of CEO’s who start their career which sparks a debate with him and MC Eiht you must hear!
